title.en-US: All recreation centers in Berlin are closed until further notice

slug.en-US: All recreation centers in Berlin are closed until further notice

teaser.en-US: Effective on March 16, 2020 all Community Recreation Center locations will be closed.

content.value:
Effective on March 16, 2020 all Community Recreation Center locations will be closed. This is part of a city-wide decision to close fitness centers to curb the spread of Covid-19 by limiting social contact. 

The health and safety of our employees and our community is of upmost importance. 

We all have a responsibility to contain the spread of COVID-19. We will regularly update this page as the situation unfolds. Please check back for updates.

description.en-US: This is a demo example. This solution enables organizations to quickly and easily publish a website. We hope to help communities stay better informed and connected in the midst of closures and quarantine.
